data.description: Welcome to your charming new abode!  This delightful 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathrooms home offers a cozy retreat nestled on a spacious corner lot.  With 1841 square feet of living space, there's plenty of room for your family to spread out and relax.  Convenience meets practicality with an upstairs laundry room, making chores a breeze.  The backyard is a tranquil haven, backing up to a lush green area for added privacy and serenity.  Recently upgraded with a 50 year roof and solar panels, this home not only boasts durability but also energy efficiency, saving you money on utility bills.  Located minutes away from local winery's and public schools, this property offers the perfect balance of peaceful living and accessibility to amenities.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this lovely home yours!
